Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.83,0:22:33.73,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}all the world is stereotypical
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.81,0:22:34.78,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}They're Playing out rules
