Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.79,0:22:49.13,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}( ONE )
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:51.55,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Because your soul is what you were BORN TO BE
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.61,0:22:55.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}たとえ今まで生きるstrategy 夢失っても　
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.46,0:22:56.48,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}(It's time now)
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.60,0:22:58.86,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}ハンドルを切って暴れ行く
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.86,0:23:01.11,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}夢のまま突き進め
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.51,0:23:03.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}冬のない人生に挑むなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.07,0:23:06.40,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}忍のない感情を抱くなら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.57,0:23:08.64,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}覚悟決めて行くんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.65,0:23:11.62,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}自分自身をbreak away
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.44,0:23:16.16,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}全てを奪われる運命なら
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.25,0:23:18.82,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}何を信じて生きていくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.83,0:23:23.71,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ask yourself, the way there's nothing to live or die for
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.78,0:23:26.24,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}過去も傷も恐れるなら
